{"tid":2010172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"研究發現16%男性確診者精液有病毒　包括康復中病人","createTime":"2020-05-10T08:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T09:17:33.000Z","uid":66271,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"46d0174f30c37ae96f6c7649c8dc5636c10e2328","tid":2010172,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200508/335412138921299968.jpeg/uoqOrkoFYwQXqv_Xb95bSw84wiWI8bqScWTxEHFk8RA?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200508%2F335412138921299968.jpeg%2FuoqOrkoFYwQXqv_Xb95bSw84wiWI8bqScWTxEHFk8RA%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=72c86b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n河南省商丘市立醫院研究人員針對38名15至50歲新冠肺炎男性病患進行研究，發現16%病患中的精液含有新冠病毒。6名病人中，4人仍受感染，2人處於康復期。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員表示，因研究樣本數目少、研究結果為初步發現，仍需要更多研究證實性行為是否在新冠肺炎疫情中扮演傳播病毒的關鍵因素。<br />\n<br />\n這項5月7日發表在《美國醫學會雜誌・網絡開放》期刊的研究指出，「關於病毒脫落、存活時間及在精液中的濃度需要更進一步的研究。如果能夠證實新冠病毒會透過性行為傳播，這可能是預防的重要關鍵。尤其是考量到復原中病患的精液中也含有新冠病毒」。<br />\n<br />\n其他科學家表示，研究結果很有趣，但必須謹慎檢視。其他小型研究並沒有發現新冠肺炎病患的精液中有病毒存在。"},{"pid":"00aff0b58afda371b0cec16210e8e3dfd187b3da","tid":2010172,"uid":62532,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:55:23.000Z","msg":"環球：官方全面嚴格實施禁止口爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36da5fe2aea89035019b63d663ced809a8654dce","tid":2010172,"uid":275238,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:55:31.000Z","msg":"人類滅絕計劃"},{"pid":"41383e3190c26e54ea248609ba8ba166c3bd7406","tid":2010172,"uid":46587,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/wxVqqtL.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"3eb488a6403b4aa74b02d71c50246a4ea7e948e6","tid":2010172,"uid":126046,"like":0,"dislike":0,